": "ısınmak", "id": "hangat", "bn": "গরম হওয়া", "es": "calentarse", "fr": "se réchauffer", "de": "sich wärmen", "ru": "согреться", "zh": "取暖"}, "definition": null, "etymology": null, "ipa": null, "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n24826", "headword_ar": "اصطلى", "root": "SlY", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He warmed himself"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biAln~aAri", "text_ar": "بِالنَّارِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by means of the fire"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (M:) one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AiSoTalayotu", "text_ar": "اِصْطَلَيْتُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biAln~aAri", "text_ar": "بِالنَّارِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bihaA", "text_ar": "بِهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taSal~ayotu", "text_ar": "تَصَلَّيْتُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[app. meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I warmed myself by means of the fire"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (S:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ASTlY Aln~aAra", "text_ar": "اصطلى النَّارَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biAln~aAri", "text_ar": "بِالنَّارِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "mean"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he became warm by means of the fire:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biAln~aAri", "text_ar": "بِالنَّارِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tSl~Y", "text_ar": "تصلّى", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he became burnt by the fire."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(MA.) Hence, in the Kur [xxvii. 7 and xxviii. 29],"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laEal~akumo taSoTaluwna", "text_ar": "لَعَلَّكُمْ تَصْطَلُونَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "May-be ye will warm yourselves"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (TA:) in relation to which it is said that the time was winter, and therefore"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlAiSoTilaA='", "text_ar": "الاِصْطِلَا=ء"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "was needed. (M, TA.) ―         -b2-  It is also said of the chameleon, as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He repaired to the sun."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M and L in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$q*", "text_ar": "شقذ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": see an ex. in a verse cited voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$aqa*aAnN", "text_ar": "شَقَذَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) ―         -b3-  And one says of a courageous man, with whom one cannot cope,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA yuSoTalaY binaArihi", "text_ar": "لَا يُصْطَلَى بِنَارِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[lit."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "One cannot warm himself by means of his fire;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "one cannot approach him when he is inflamed with rage,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "especially"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in fight,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "battle"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S.) The phrase may be also used satirically, as meaning (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "One will not seek his hospitality."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Meyd. [See Freytag's Arab. Prov. ii. 588.]) ―         -b4-  See also 1, latter half, in two places."}], "source_refs": ["M", "K", "S", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}